casebody.data:
William Thomas ZEIGLER, Jr., petitioner,
v.
FLORIDA. No. 13-6291. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 16, 2013.

Case below, 116 So.3d 255.

Motion of petitioner to defer consideration of the petition for writ of certiorari denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Florida denied.
